properties.textfield: The program has a move gripper action that grabs the "blade" thing
The program contains a move gripper action for grabbing the "blade" thing and there are not thing flow errors in the review panel.
Open the location drawer and create a new location. Select and edit the new location, moving its position to: 1, -1, 0.3
